to board the plane

1042
01:06:46,736 --> 01:06:49,438
and prove otherwise.

1043
01:06:49,439 --> 01:06:50,038
We need to clean up...

1044
01:06:54,043 --> 01:06:56,578
this...

1045
01:06:56,579 --> 01:06:59,314
Clean yourselves.

1046
01:06:59,315 --> 01:07:02,518
We need to clean up
and cover up.

1047
01:07:02,519 --> 01:07:06,255
Can you pick him up?

1048
01:07:06,256 --> 01:07:08,056
Sit him down here.

1049
01:07:08,057 --> 01:07:11,460
He needs to go
on this chair.

1050
01:07:11,461 --> 01:07:11,727
Frank, could you come
with me, please?

1051
01:07:15,732 --> 01:07:17,466
Frank?

1052
01:07:17,467 --> 01:07:20,068
We have nothing more
to talk about.

1053
01:07:20,069 --> 01:07:22,070
I haven't said everything
I needed to.

1054
01:07:22,071 --> 01:07:26,208
Come.

1055
01:07:26,209 --> 01:07:27,743
Well I have.
Fuck off! I'm not asking you.
I'm telling you.

1056
01:07:27,744 --> 01:07:30,812
Frank, come!

1057
01:07:34,751 --> 01:07:37,653
The liaison is ready,
but before we send him in,

1058
01:07:37,654 --> 01:07:39,221
