to uncover the windows.

1059
01:07:39,222 --> 01:07:42,090
We're making progress
on the money.

1060
01:07:42,091 --> 01:07:45,627
There's a small addendum
to the money request,

1061
01:07:45,628 --> 01:07:47,496
I want it given in full

1062
01:07:47,497 --> 01:07:51,433
to the Kips Bay
Children's Outreach Fund.

1063
01:07:51,434 --> 01:07:53,101
That's K-I-P-S Bay
Children's Outreach Fund.

1064
01:07:57,640 --> 01:08:00,809
This will be
our last communication

1065
01:08:00,810 --> 01:08:03,412
until I get
takeoff clearance.

1066
01:08:03,413 --> 01:08:04,479
Well, we're just now getting

1067
01:08:06,149 --> 01:08:09,151
our first live look
at the situation,

1068
01:08:09,152 --> 01:08:10,385
but we have just received word
that our own Ian Finley

1069
01:08:15,158 --> 01:08:17,693
will in fact be allowed
on to the plane

1070
01:08:17,694 --> 01:08:21,296
to confirm the condition
of the hostages through video.

1071
01:08:24,267 --> 01:08:28,270
Kips Bay?

1072
01:08:28,271 --> 01:08:31,807
Children's Outreach Fund?

1073
01:08:31,808 --> 01:08:33,408
Bullshit!

1074
01:08:33,409 --> 01:08:34,610
You have very good hearing.

1075
01:08:34,611 --> 01:08:37,546
Listen,
stop fucking with me, okay?

1076
01:08:37,547 --> 01:08:40,282
Two of my friends are dead
and I want answers.

1077
01:08:40,283 --> 01:08:42,284
You owe me answers.

1078
01:08:49,826 --> 01:08:52,561
Mr. O'Connell...

1079
01:08:52,562 --> 01:08:55,597
You don't negotiate for us. We can't pay 5 million dollars
live on our own network.

1080
01:08:55,598 --> 01:08:56,865
Sir, you won't have to.

1081
01:08:56,866 --> 01:08:58,867
The liaison
is just to get us in.

1082
01:08:58,868 --> 01:09:00,869
Finley's not even
an ANC employee.

1083
01:09:00,870 --> 01:09:03,805
He's just there
as a personal favor for us.

1084
01:09:03,806 --> 01:09:06,208
There are only two plays here,
Mr. O'Connell.

1085
01:09:06,209 --> 01:09:08,377
You pay the money
or we send in your man.

1086
01:09:08,378 --> 01:09:09,177
Your choice.

1087
01:09:11,481 --> 01:09:13,649
You just make sure
he is safe.

1088
01:09:21,624 --> 01:09:25,360
This fund.
It's a front, isn't it?

1089
01:09:25,361 --> 01:09:27,763
A front for what?

1090
01:09:27,764 --> 01:09:31,767
It's for
a very powerful attorney.

1091
01:09:31,768 --> 01:09:33,769
What the hell
do you need a lawyer for?

1092
01:09:33,770 --> 01:09:35,370
Frank, I need you to know

1093
01:09:35,371 --> 01:09:37,339
