was not planned.

1094
01:09:37,340 --> 01:09:40,409
Fuck you!
Don't call me Frank!

1095
01:09:44,614 --> 01:09:47,482
Kips Bay,
that's in New York.

1096
01:09:47,483 --> 01:09:49,885
The kid
in the network story.

1097
01:09:49,886 --> 01:09:52,621
That's what the expensive
lawyer is for, isn't it?

1098
01:09:52,622 --> 01:09:56,491
Is that
what this is all about?

1099
01:09:56,492 --> 01:09:57,459
America does not negotiate
with terrorists or pirates.

1100
01:10:02,498 --> 01:10:06,234
I couldn't take someone hostage
and demand his release.

1101
01:10:06,235 --> 01:10:09,438
I need to have him
acquitted by law.

1102
01:10:09,439 --> 01:10:14,209
What do you care?

1103
01:10:14,210 --> 01:10:15,510
It's just like the kid
in the back.When I asked you earlier

1104
01:10:15,511 --> 01:10:17,779
