I thought to myself secretly,

1106
01:10:20,516 --> 01:10:23,785
he must be his little brother
or something?

1107
01:10:23,786 --> 01:10:27,255
The kid back there isn't
your little brother...

1108
01:10:27,256 --> 01:10:28,790
Mateo Wal-i-Musi is, right?

1109
01:10:30,893 --> 01:10:33,662
You wanted an interview,
you got an interview!

1110
01:10:36,666 --> 01:10:38,266
Answer
the fucking question!

1111
01:10:38,267 --> 01:10:40,936
Yes.

1112
01:10:40,937 --> 01:10:45,407
My brother Mateo is on trial
in New York City,

1113
01:10:45,408 --> 01:10:47,676
but in the jury's mind
he is already guilty

1114
01:10:47,677 --> 01:10:49,411
because your network's piece

1115
01:10:49,412 --> 01:10:52,347
made him the poster boy
for piracy in America.

1116
01:10:52,348 --> 01:10:53,882
So this is revenge
against the network?

1117
01:10:53,883 --> 01:10:55,350
No, it's not
about revenge;

1118
01:10:55,351 --> 01:10:56,752
it's about re-education.

1119
01:10:56,753 --> 01:10:58,420
Your network wanted
to investigate

1120
01:10:58,421 --> 01:11:00,655
how a boy could be involved
in such atrocities?

1121
01:11:00,656 --> 01:11:03,658
Well, I have shown you here,
firsthand.

1122
01:11:03,659 --> 01:11:06,261
Let me get this straight.

1123
01:11:06,262 --> 01:11:09,931
So, you're not really
a pirate, are you?

1124
01:11:09,932 --> 01:11:10,398
No.

1125
01:11:12,635 --> 01:11:14,536
I left Somalia

1126
01:11:17,607 --> 01:11:20,942
