was still a baby.

1127
01:11:20,943 --> 01:11:24,713
Off to better myself.

1128
01:11:24,714 --> 01:11:26,314
By the time I got back

1129
01:11:26,315 --> 01:11:29,417
he was already taking orders
from those two.

1130
01:11:29,418 --> 01:11:31,553
There was nothing I could do.

1131
01:11:31,554 --> 01:11:33,421
When he was captured
on that ship,

1132
01:11:33,422 --> 01:11:38,293
they fled and set him up
to take the blame.

1133
01:11:38,294 --> 01:11:40,962
So, this whole thing
is a trap for them.

1134
01:11:40,963 --> 01:11:42,831
Something like that.

1135
01:11:42,832 --> 01:11:44,666
And they don't know
who you are!

1136
01:11:44,667 --> 01:11:46,935
Oh, they will.

1137
01:11:46,936 --> 01:11:49,938
They will.

1138
01:11:49,939 --> 01:11:52,941
Why film everything?

1139
01:11:52,942 --> 01:11:55,076
When America sees
that skinny boy in the back,

1140
01:11:55,077 --> 01:11:58,346
they will see my brother too.

1141
01:11:58,347 --> 01:12:02,083
The abuse he endured.

1142
01:12:02,084 --> 01:12:04,019
How they cornered
a helpless child

1143
01:12:04,020 --> 01:12:06,521
and make him do
unspeakable things

1144
01:12:06,522 --> 01:12:08,523
for their own gain.

1145
01:12:08,524 --> 01:12:10,058
In other words...

1146
01:12:10,059 --> 01:12:12,527
exactly what you've done
to this kid!

1147
01:12:12,528 --> 01:12:14,830
I don't understand,
you blame these two

1148
01:12:14,831 --> 01:12:17,933
for having made your brother,
but who made them?

1149
01:12:17,934 --> 01:12:20,802
I mean, aren't they somebody's
fucked up little brothers, too?

1150
01:12:20,803 --> 01:12:23,738
Where does it end?

1151
01:12:23,739 --> 01:12:25,674
That kid killed
one of my colleagues.

1152
01:12:29,812 --> 01:12:30,812
If he is supposed to be
the mirror image of Mateo,

1153
01:12:35,551 --> 01:12:38,687
what does it do
for your brother?

1154
01:12:38,688 --> 01:12:41,823
How does it
make him look?

1155
01:12:41,824 --> 01:12:44,693
Makes him look
like a killer.

1156
01:12:44,694 --> 01:12:46,628
- Do not deviate.
- Finley, you're crazy, man!

1157
01:12:46,629 --> 01:12:48,530
Can I ask any questions?

1158
01:12:51,801 --> 01:12:54,102
Only if you allow them,
okay?

1159
01:12:54,103 --> 01:12:57,806
So what are the assurances
that he'll let us leave?

1160
01:13:01,711 --> 01:13:04,512
Ian Finley and his cameraman

1161
01:13:04,513 --> 01:13:08,683
obviously approaching
with great caution.

1162
01:13:08,684 --> 01:13:11,987
I just realized

1163
01:13:11,988 --> 01:13:12,754
I forgot to get my sister
a souvenir. We'll pick one up in Nairobi.

1164
01:13:15,091 --> 01:13:17,592
And so what if America
sees this footage

1165
01:13:19,695 --> 01:13:21,563
and they decide
that that kid back there,

1166
01:13:21,564 --> 01:13:22,964
and therefore
your brother,

1167
01:13:22,965 --> 01:13:25,967
is to be held responsible,

1168
01:13:25,968 --> 01:13:28,703
because they
were taken advantage of,

1169
01:13:28,704 --> 01:13:30,705
and that's not right,

1170
01:13:30,706 --> 01:13:31,706
but ultimately,
they made the choice.

1171
01:13:35,711 --> 01:13:39,447
Really?

1172
01:13:39,448 --> 01:13:40,982
In which case,

1173
01:13:40,983 --> 01:13:45,120
I would like you to share
with America right now,

1174
01:13:45,121 --> 01:13:45,787
why you made the choice
to stab that pilot.

1175
01:13:53,729 --> 01:13:54,529
Diagnose your motivations
for the camera, please.

1176
01:14:08,077 --> 01:14:10,078
What's stopping me
from telling your friends

1177
01:14:10,079 --> 01:14:10,478
you're going to hang
them all out to dry?

1178
01:14:14,684 --> 01:14:16,217
Even if you could,

1179
01:14:16,218 --> 01:14:19,754
it would be
mutually assured destruction.

1180
01:14:24,093 --> 01:14:27,829
I'm just curious...

1181
01:14:27,830 --> 01:14:30,832
if you're not a pirate
by occupation,

1182
01:14:30,833 --> 01:14:32,167
what are you;
I mean, before today?

1183
01:14:53,055 --> 01:14:56,925
Well...

1184
01:14:56,926 --> 01:15:00,061
I am a schoolteacher.

1185
01:15:11,273 --> 01:15:13,675
Frank...go to the back

1186
01:15:18,214 --> 01:15:20,081
and be smart.

1187
01:15:45,775 --> 01:15:48,910
And as you can see
on your screen now,

1188
01:15:51,013 --> 01:15:53,882
they've just opened the door,
that's the first time

1189
01:15:53,883 --> 01:15:56,885
since the plane
was taken hours ago.

1190
01:16:04,727 --> 01:16:05,660
Come.

1191
01:16:07,897 --> 01:16:10,065
Is he a cop?
I don't know!

1192
01:16:13,669 --> 01:16:15,070
Should we say something
to him?

1193
01:16:15,071 --> 01:16:16,738
I mean,
we gotta let him know...

1194
01:16:16,739 --> 01:16:20,642
No.
Let's see what happens.

1195
01:16:40,162 --> 01:16:43,898
I was told that there were
more than three hostages.

1196
01:16:43,899 --> 01:16:45,667
You mean more than three
white hostages?

1197
01:16:45,668 --> 01:16:47,168
No, I meant passengers.

1198
01:16:47,169 --> 01:16:49,170
What about the African crew?
Are they not hostages?

1199
01:16:49,171 --> 01:16:52,140
Yes, of course they are,
but that's not what I meant.

1200
01:16:52,141 --> 01:16:56,044
Just...

1201
01:16:56,045 --> 01:16:57,912
Can I just speak
to one of them please? You have two minutes.

1202
01:16:57,913 --> 01:17:02,350
Please.

1203
01:17:02,351 --> 01:17:06,187
Sir, are you the captain?

1204
01:17:06,188 --> 01:17:07,789
I am.

1205
01:17:07,790 --> 01:17:11,192
How many passengers
boarded the plane?

1206
01:17:11,193 --> 01:17:14,295
However many you see here.

1207
01:17:14,296 --> 01:17:16,197
How about asking one
of the non-African hostages,

1208
01:17:18,934 --> 01:17:20,869
since you like
to make the distinction.

1209
01:17:20,870 --> 01:17:23,671
No, actually...
I think we're okay.

1210
01:17:23,672 --> 01:17:24,939
I'm just going to...

1211
01:17:24,940 --> 01:17:26,341
if I may...
continue...

1212
01:17:26,342 --> 01:17:29,644
Make it quick.

1213
01:17:41,957 --> 01:17:43,791
Why are you allowing them
to film,

1214
01:17:43,792 --> 01:17:45,059
if you don't mind my asking?

1215
01:17:45,060 --> 01:17:48,830
It's none of your business.

1216
01:17:48,831 --> 01:17:51,833
You have one more minute.

1217
01:18:01,911 --> 01:18:04,045
Just to reiterate
if you've just tuned in,

1218
01:18:04,046 --> 01:18:08,316
