inside the plane at this time.

1219
01:18:08,317 --> 01:18:12,053
We're going to have to wait
for Ian and his cameraman.

1220
01:18:12,054 --> 01:18:12,854
It's been about
three minutes so far.

1221
01:18:30,873 --> 01:18:33,875
As you can see,
