1222
01:18:39,882 --> 01:18:42,283
Okay, Finley, let's go.

1223
01:18:42,284 --> 01:18:43,751
Let's go.

1224
01:18:43,752 --> 01:18:45,887
Go, go.

1225
01:18:45,888 --> 01:18:48,289
