1285
01:23:28,337 --> 01:23:28,469
No...

1286
01:23:32,608 --> 01:23:33,207
I don't know!

1287
01:23:34,276 --> 01:23:37,345
Okay, go, go.

1288
01:24:05,741 --> 01:24:09,410
Everybody down!
Everybody down!

1289
01:24:25,694 --> 01:24:28,663
Hey, hey!

1290
01:24:34,269 --> 01:24:35,670
Ladies and gentlemen...

1291
01:24:35,671 --> 01:24:38,673
I recommend that if you find

1292
